  "time_ut": 1658389743,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0b85\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb2\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Vimal exposed those responsible for Ranil's presidency",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Why didn't we say that the President should resign before the Presidential Secretariat and the Presidential Palace were surrounded? Vimal Weerawansa, leader of the National Freedom Front and MP questioned, if the incumbent leaves. He said it is because the position can be filled with someone worse than that.",
        "It is an act of anarchy. The young protestors did not understand it. \"I don't think they were smart enough to think,\" he said.",
        "Speaking at a press conference held today (21) in Colombo, he said what happened in the end. The President, who did not order firing on the protesters while encircling the Presidential Palace, has gone home. The man who tried to feed the protesters became president.",
        "Ranil Wickremesinghe became the President as a result of a 'struggle' without strategy or vision and one who paralyzed the protesters themselves.",
        "Why did you vote for Ranil? Lack of security for MPs. First of all, this condition should be eliminated. Who can do it? Ranil Wickramasinghe, who created that mood? said the protesters.",
        "Ranil Wickramasinghe, who was the attacker, ordered the security forces to implement emergency law and curfew law when the group including Lalkanta, Sunil Handhunedhi tried to turn Parliament into another presidential secretariat, presidential palace, and that same person has been appointed as the president today.",
        "Those with pierced ears, those with beards and their hair in disarray were those who had no political purpose or future purpose. By becoming players, telling stories and campaigning through social media, the actors have created this situation together."
      ],
